# 止蝕
(pos:動詞)
<explanation>
yue:投資或者炒股嗰陣，當價錢跌到某個預設嘅位，就主動賣出嚟限制虧損，唔好令蝕錢嘅情況繼續擴大（量詞：次）
eng:to cut losses; to stop loss
<eg>
yue:隻股跌咗咁多，你仲唔止蝕，想蝕到連褲都冇得著呀？ (zek3 gu2 dit6 zo2 gam3 do1, nei5 zung6 m4 zi2 sit6, soeng2 sit6 dou3 lin4 fu3 dou1 mou5 dak1 zoek3 aa3?)
eng:The stock has fallen so much; if you still don't cut your losses, do you want to lose everything down to your pants? [end of text]


